data.description: ****JUST REDUCED!!****CHECK OUT THIS GORGEOUS FOUR BEDROOM, FOUR & A HALF BATH COLONIAL! OVER 5,300 FINISHED SQFT OF BEAUTY SITUATED ON A 3.17-ACRE LOT IN STAFFORD'S BROOKESMILL ESTATES! LOVELY CURB APPEAL TO COME HOME TO EACH DAY WITH THE MAGNIFICENT BRICK FRONT, LARGE GARDEN BEDS READY FOR YOUR PERSONAL TOUCH, AN ENORMOUS FRONT YARD, AS WELL AS THE ATTACHED, SIDE-LOADING THREE-CAR GARAGE & AN OVERSIZED PARKING PAD & EXTENDED PAVED DRIVEWAY FOR AMPLE ADDITIONAL PARKING! LOOK FORWARD TO ENTERTAINING & RELAXING ON YOUR NIGHTS & WEEKENDS OUT BACK ON THE HUGE REAR DECK WITH A SPACIOUS, STAMPED CONCRETE PATIO BENEATH, GIVING YOU & YOUR GUESTS LOADS OF SPACE TO KICK BACK, ALL WHILE LOOKING OUT OVER THE FENCED BACKYARD & DELIGHTFUL WOODED VIEWS! THROUGH THE FRONT DOOR, YOU'RE WELCOMED BY A SOARING, TWO-STORY FOYER WITH CHANDELIER LIGHTING, CHAIR RAILING & A LARGE PALLADIAN WINDOW, AS WELL AS BEAUTIFUL HARDWOOD FLOORS THAT FLOW THROUGHOUT THE MAJORITY OF THE MAIN LEVEL! LEFT OF THE FOYER, A LARGE, FORMAL LIVING ROOM & OPPOSITE THAT, A VERY SPACIOUS FORMAL DINING ROOM WITH DOUBLE DOORS FROM THE FOYER FOR A MORE PRIVATE DINING EXPERIENCE! FROM THE DINING ROOM, A CONVENIENT BUTLER'S PANTRY WITH COUNTERTOP & CABINET STORAGE & A BUILT-IN WINE RACK! HUGE GOURMET KITCHEN WITH A WEALTH OF COUNTERTOP SPACE THAT INCLUDES AN OVERSIZED CENTER ISLAND WITH A GAS COOKTOP, STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES WITH A WALL OVEN & MICROWAVE, TONS OF CABINET STORAGE & A VERY SPACIOUS BREAKFAST ROOM WITH FRENCH DOORS TO THE REAR DECK, ALL ON TOP OF SPLENDID CERAMIC TILE FLOORING! SEPARATE LAUNDRY ROOM & GARAGE ACCESS OFF THE KITCHEN! EXTRAORDINARY FAMILY ROOM DISPLAYS A TOWERING TWO-STORY CEILING & AN ORNATE WALL OF WINDOWS TO THE WOODED REAR, PERCHED ABOVE AN EXTRAVAGANT GAS FIREPLACE — THE PERFECT SPOT TO ENJOY DAY-TO-DAY LIVING & ENTERTAIN INDOORS FOR A TRULY WELCOMING ATMOSPHERE! LARGE, PRIVATE OFFICE ON THE MAIN LEVEL WITH A WINDOW BUMP-OUT  TO THE WOODED REAR, CHAIR RAILING & A SET OF FRENCH DOORS TO COMFORTABLY WORK FROM HOME! ENORMOUS OWNER'S SUITE WITH HIGH CEILINGS & A LARGE SITTING AREA TO ENJOY YOUR OWN PRIVATE GAS FIREPLACE IN THE EVENINGS, TWO SEPARATE WALK-IN CLOSETS & A DOUBLE DOOR ENTRY TO THE LARGE ENSUITE BOASTING AN OVERSIZED SHOWER, A SOAKING TUB WITH CUSTOM TILING & HIGH CEILINGS, DOUBLE VANITY SINKS, PRIVATE WATER CLOSET & CERAMIC TILE FLOORING! THE UPPER LEVEL IS COMPLETE WITH THE REMAINING THREE SPACIOUS BEDROOMS, ONE WITH ITS OWN ATTACHED FULL BATH, A FULL HALL BATH, SECOND STORY OVERLOOK TO THE FOYER & FAMILY ROOM, AS WELL AS TWO SEPARATE STAIRCASES TO THE MAIN LEVEL! FINISHED, WALKOUT BASEMENT INCLUDES A HUGE REC ROOM WITH FRENCH DOORS TO THE REAR PATIO, A LARGE BONUS ROOM OR OPTIONAL FIFTH BEDROOM (NTC), A FULL HALL BATH & TWO LARGE STORAGE ROOMS! DO NOT MISS YOUR OPPORTUNITY TO OWN THIS MAGNIFICENT HOME WITH 5,300+ FINISHED SQFT ON 3+ ACRES IN STAFFORD! CALL TODAY TO SCHEDULE YOUR SHOWING BEFORE IT'S TOO LATE!
